Herbert Scott was one of the bright stars of the Class of 1970 of St Augustine’s College.He was an active member of St George’s Anglican Church and a founder of the singing group of Anglican Men called the Sons of Thunder. Sadly he passed away after a long illness.He was buried from Christ Church Cathedral on Saturday 5th December.The photos were taken from the Facebook page of Adrian Archer.
